================================================================================
FOUNDATION MODELS EVALUATED (weights downloaded at runtime, not redistributed)
================================================================================

- REVE (REVE-Base) — El Ouahidi et al., NeurIPS 2025 (arXiv:2510.21585).
  Weights: Hugging Face `brain-bzh/reve-base`. Loaded via transformers with
  trust_remote_code=True (upstream modeling code is fetched and executed at
  runtime; see that model card for its license).
- LaBraM — Jiang et al., ICLR 2024 (github.com/935963004/LaBraM).
  Weights: `braindecode/labram-pretrained`.
- BENDR — Kostas et al., Frontiers in Human Neuroscience 2021
  (github.com/SPOClab-ca/BENDR). Weights: `braindecode/braindecode-bendr`.
- CBraMod — Wang et al., ICLR 2025 (see attribution above).
  Weights: `weighting666/CBraMod`.
- BIOT — Yang et al., NeurIPS 2023 (github.com/ycq091044/BIOT).
  Weights: `braindecode/biot-pretrained-six-datasets-18chs`.

